snippet.title: Free Indie Game - Creative Console Trailer
snippet.description:
"Take control of all game elements! By selecting Creative Cards, you can change the camera angle, place objects, switch skins, summon enemies, and even create a football match. Becoming an outstanding game designer, creating unique levels and gameplay, with unlimited creativity awaits you."

Steam Page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2070880/Creative_Console/
